Dotfiles
--------

Config files.

Managed as a bare git repo.


Software
--------

 OS:                 https://www.artixlinux.org/
 Window manager:     https://git.sr.ht/~ttr3dp/dwm
 Statusbar:          https://tools.suckless.org/slstatus
 Terminal:           https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty
 Launcher:           https://git.sr.ht/~ttr3dp/dmenu
 Shell:              http://zsh.sourceforge.net/
 Editor:             https://neovim.io/
 Video player:       https://mpv.io/
 Music player:       https://cmus.github.io/
 File manager:       NONE
 Web browser         https://librewolf-community.gitlab.io/
 PDF viewer:         https://pwmt.org/projects/zathura/
 Image viewer:       https://github.com/muennich/sxiv
 Fonts:              https://git.sr.ht/~ttr3dp/dots/blob/master/.config/fontconfig/fonts.conf
 Notifications:      https://git.sr.ht/~ttr3dp/herbe
 Composite manager:  https://github.com/yshui/picom
 Torrent client:     https://github.com/tremc/tremc
